						<p>
				What is Defi Crypto Aside from decentralized gaming, trading, and gambling platforms, decentralized finance, or DeFi, is a new monetary protocol that uses blockchain to enable investors to accomplish new and old things with their money while reaping a whole slew of new benefits. Traditional banking is fairly costly.			</p>

